name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 60: Feels bad in the city

content.html:
Dear Internet, On this weeks show, watching riverdale, a city wide event of just feeling odd, and we decide what to do with the extra room. Just a heads up, no new episode next week due to scheduling issues, but there will be a patreon. Stay gold, XOXO We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
